@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pasavo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.49
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.84) / v1)
    v0 = wp.abs(0.66)
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.51) * (v2 + 0.94 * tmp + 0.34)))
    v2 = 0.59
    data[tid] = v0
